<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>264</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa, Na vangsakna lopi
 Tuhin ka chang kit tau
 Ka khut tawmuh vang Na pie a
 Temple hawih Na In sak na'n.

[V2]
 Lalpa Jeho Na min lopina ding
 Na thagau Thiengtho in ei hung luohpih in
 Na In thiengtho hung hi hen la,
 Hung chengin Nang di'n ka pieu.

[V3]
 2. Aw nanga dinga semgim te'n
 Kipahman chang u nau
 Tu a patin kumsawt chanin
 A kipahnau sang ina.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa zie In lopi ahin
 Thupha ka hun chawih un
 Na ngaihdamna Aw hawih tak chun
 Ei dawngin. Na In ahin

[V5]
 4. Thagau chau di'n chawlhna In nuom
 Van guol a vakna ah
 Gilkiel, dangchakte lut unau,
 Kumsawt kipahna mun au.</lyrics>
<title>Na Min Lopina Ding</title>
</song>